WEBVTT

00:00:10.110 --> 00:00:16.000
In this world like nuts packed in a bag,

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:22.880
Everyone is snuggling up
to someone they meet

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:28.990
We are mixed in there and smiling

00:00:28.990 --> 00:00:34.680
By pretending we are
all nuts like peanuts

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:37.650
On the template of happiness,

00:00:37.650 --> 00:00:41.050
Behind the surface
which is literally picturesque

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:45.450
We can't be as we are,

00:00:45.450 --> 00:00:50.820
Even when we put our hands
together sitting around a table

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:58.120
Home with full of secrets
and patches, you know?

00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:00.830
Even though I chew up
the real emotions,

00:01:00.830 --> 00:01:04.110
they still don't disappear

00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:05.650
They are still stuck in my teeth

00:01:05.650 --> 00:01:08.590
My life is so insecure and drifting,

00:01:08.590 --> 00:01:10.800
And I know

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:14.320
Every day is so mediocre,

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:18.930
but I'm here and so are you

00:01:18.930 --> 00:01:25.400
Just by this truth,
my stomach feels heavy

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:37.580
(Mission: 11 - Stella)

00:01:38.740 --> 00:01:41.500
No way... All our pursuers are...

00:01:42.130 --> 00:01:44.180
Let's go back to the
hideout and rethink our steps.

00:01:44.970 --> 00:01:46.610
I have a bad feeling about this.

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:51.510
N-No way...!

00:01:51.940 --> 00:01:54.940
How can this be possible, Bondman?!

00:01:54.940 --> 00:01:57.190
Ugh... How could I let this slide?!

00:01:57.190 --> 00:01:58.880
- Hey, wake up! What happened?!

00:01:58.880 --> 00:01:59.960
- Hey, Anya.
- Hey, wake up! What happened?!

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:00.690
- Anya's busy now.
- Hey, wake up! What happened?!

00:02:00.690 --> 00:02:01.640
- Anya's busy now.

00:02:02.730 --> 00:02:04.430
This tragedy...

00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:07.720
Nooo!!

00:02:07.720 --> 00:02:10.180
- I hate studyiiiiing!!

00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:11.540
- Hold it right there!
- I hate studyiiiiing!!

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:14.540
I thought we agreed
to start studying at 5?

00:02:14.540 --> 00:02:16.450
Hieeehh!!

00:02:16.450 --> 00:02:17.450
A devil!

00:02:17.450 --> 00:02:20.190
- You're a devil, Father!
- Operation Strix: Phase 2.

00:02:21.320 --> 00:02:24.450
In order for me to participate in
my target's social gathering,

00:02:24.450 --> 00:02:29.590
I need to turn my daughter, Anya, into
a scholarship student, an Imperial Scholar.

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:33.560
And for that, she needs to
achieve excellent academic performances...

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:36.250
...in order for her to earn a Stella.

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:45.140
How many times do I have to tell you?

00:02:45.460 --> 00:02:47.610
The answer for that isn't A, but E.

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:52.070
B-But, Loid...

00:02:52.070 --> 00:02:54.500
Anya scored pretty good in maths.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.990
Well done, Anya.

00:02:57.660 --> 00:02:59.990
I only have 2/8 rounds left!

00:03:00.580 --> 00:03:01.870
Was it from watching the cartoon?

00:03:02.230 --> 00:03:03.520
Oh, right.

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:08.000
This proverb is the same
one Bondman said in Episode 16!

00:03:09.370 --> 00:03:10.470
I forgot.

00:03:10.470 --> 00:03:11.840
Try to remember it!

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.940
Come on, it's the episode where the
man with sideburns appeared...

00:03:14.940 --> 00:03:20.390
I just happened to read the wrong
minds to cheat during the exams.

00:03:20.610 --> 00:03:22.660
I'll just take my time...

00:03:22.660 --> 00:03:27.410
...to see for myself to decide
who's best at which subject,

00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:31.420
and then I'll definitely get
a perfect score in every subject.

00:03:31.420 --> 00:03:32.840
No sweat.

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:36.060
I tried saying it like Father.

00:03:37.090 --> 00:03:41.160
Sure, I could just forge her
scores to A+ behind the scene easily,

00:03:41.900 --> 00:03:44.090
but if she suddenly got
good scores overnight,

00:03:44.090 --> 00:03:46.820
the school and the people
around her would be suspicious.

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.660
In order to naturally disguise the forgery,

00:03:49.660 --> 00:03:52.170
she must improve
her basic academic skills first.

00:03:53.130 --> 00:03:58.160
If she becomes estranged from her friends,
her school life may suffer as well.

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:01.230
- I can't have her refuse to go to school...
- If I read my friends' minds

00:04:01.230 --> 00:04:02.280
- and get perfect scores,

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:04.300
they'll hate me...

00:04:04.910 --> 00:04:07.750
How could you possibly know that?!

00:04:07.750 --> 00:04:09.690
You creepy little witch!

00:04:13.600 --> 00:04:16.410
I guess I was too harsh
in enforcing her to study.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.740
When her motivation to study is low,

00:04:19.740 --> 00:04:23.100
her focus will never improve,
resulting in slumped learning efficiency.

00:04:23.100 --> 00:04:25.010
It's always good to make a change.

00:04:25.010 --> 00:04:27.710
Academics aren't
the only field to obtain a Stella.

00:04:29.890 --> 00:04:30.710
All right.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:33.640
Let's take a break
and draw pictures instead.

00:04:35.930 --> 00:04:37.210
For instance, arts.

00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:39.720
Wow, that's a cool drawing.

00:04:40.340 --> 00:04:41.320
Is it a cheetah?

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:42.810
Oh, wait.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:44.630
