00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.730
It's a cow, the one in the school.

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:55.330
Or maybe music!

00:04:55.330 --> 00:04:57.480
Here's a violin for kids.

00:05:02.450 --> 00:05:03.990
