00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.570
Come on, don't cry.

00:05:18.570 --> 00:05:19.800
Calm down, Twilight.

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:22.140
A thousand-miles journey
begins with a single step.

00:05:22.500 --> 00:05:24.450
She's still in the first grade, too.

00:05:25.570 --> 00:05:29.970
I need to take the time to find out
her strongest suits and improve them.

00:05:29.970 --> 00:05:32.060
Should we play skipping?

00:05:32.370 --> 00:05:33.820
It'll be fun!

00:05:34.270 --> 00:05:36.170
Right, don't be so hasty.

00:05:36.620 --> 00:05:40.070
It's not like Desmond's
going to make a move this instant.

00:05:40.700 --> 00:05:44.450
Planning for war must take an
enormous amount of time.

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:46.010
However...

00:05:47.930 --> 00:05:52.460
We expect you to achieve eight
Stella Stars in about four months...

00:05:53.060 --> 00:05:56.130
