much time to spare?

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:58.410
Father...

00:05:58.940 --> 00:06:00.460
Anya will work hard!

00:06:02.840 --> 00:06:04.960
Anyway, do you mind
untangling this rope first?

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.470
Oh, right...

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.330
Hey, Anya.

00:06:09.330 --> 00:06:09.850
Hm?

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:12.010
Why don't we go for a walk tomorrow?

00:06:13.110 --> 00:06:14.270
