develop a philanthropic spirit.

00:07:08.370 --> 00:07:09.280
All right, then...

00:07:10.090 --> 00:07:14.790
I'd like you to handle the cleaning
of this changing room, Mr. Forger.

00:07:15.260 --> 00:07:16.390
There's a pool there!

00:07:16.990 --> 00:07:19.170
