00:07:22.930 --> 00:07:24.180
Ah...

00:07:25.650 --> 00:07:28.210
Perhaps it's a bit too much for you?

00:07:28.210 --> 00:07:30.940
Well, then, please arrange
the books in the library instead.

00:07:35.080 --> 00:07:37.600
Excuse me, Mister!
Come with me!

00:07:40.250 --> 00:07:42.860
Could you please do something else?

00:07:49.330 --> 00:07:51.180
Anya's tired of doing chores.

00:07:52.220 --> 00:07:54.880
