But still...

00:08:24.430 --> 00:08:28.100
If there's little hope of getting a Stella
from social contribution, what should I do...

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:30.710
Hey, is the rehab going to be tough?

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:35.130
It is, but you gotta do your
best so that you can run again!

