Father...

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.870
Anya sucks at volunteering...

00:09:57.610 --> 00:09:58.970
So...

00:10:00.100 --> 00:10:03.020
I want to become a swimmer,

00:10:03.020 --> 00:10:05.140
so I'll go practice at the pool!

00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:06.730
Huh?! Hey, wait!

00:10:06.730 --> 00:10:08.380
I told you, that pool's not for public use!

00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:13.380
Ken?

00:10:14.950 --> 00:10:17.010
Don't tell me he backed out...

00:10:17.430 --> 00:10:18.720
- Uwaaaaahh!!

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:19.810
