00:12:07.290 --> 00:12:09.340
Don't be so reckless next time.

00:12:09.340 --> 00:12:11.390
Thank you! Thank you!

00:12:11.390 --> 00:12:14.560
Good job, Miss!

00:12:30.260 --> 00:12:33.410
Anya Forger from Cecile Hall, First Year.

00:12:33.410 --> 00:12:36.740
We'll award you with
a Stella for saving a life.

00:12:42.010 --> 00:12:44.010
Way to go, Anya!

