I heard your daughter
has obtained a Stella,

00:14:02.790 --> 00:14:04.360
Agent Twilight.

00:14:04.970 --> 00:14:06.040
Yes, Handler.

00:14:06.550 --> 00:14:08.240
It's all thanks to you.

00:14:09.260 --> 00:14:10.770
At this rate,

00:14:10.770 --> 00:14:12.710
