the identity of our valuable personnel,

00:14:23.390 --> 00:14:26.010
or having them arrested.

00:14:27.150 --> 00:14:28.610
I suppose so.

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:31.690
So HQ is getting impatient now?

00:14:32.430 --> 00:14:33.110
No...

00:14:33.720 --> 00:14:36.410
But there has been an increase
in suspicious money transactions...

00:14:36.410 --> 00:14:39.000
...in some of the businesses
around Desmond.

00:14:39.910 --> 00:14:42.080
It's not an optimistic situation either.

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:45.410
Make contact with Desmond
as soon as possible.

00:14:45.790 --> 00:14:50.000
