Come to our house
with your parents next time!

00:16:03.150 --> 00:16:03.610
Bam!

00:16:04.050 --> 00:16:07.110
Well done, Anya!
My mission's complete now!

00:16:07.530 --> 00:16:09.890
The world is now at peace.

00:16:11.410 --> 00:16:13.260
Don't be so full of yourself!

00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:18.740
What the heck?! He's so annoying!

00:16:18.740 --> 00:16:20.450
It's different from what I'd planned.

00:16:20.450 --> 00:16:21.880
The world is in danger.

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:24.250
Let's go, Anya.

00:16:30.450 --> 00:16:33.380
Let's go... Starlight Anya.

00:16:33.380 --> 00:16:34.120
Yep.

00:16:35.400 --> 00:16:36.730
What a drag...

00:16:41.150 --> 00:16:42.950
Heh... What a joke.

00:16:43.430 --> 00:16:46.740
She's really full of herself, huh.

00:16:46.740 --> 00:16:49.900
Putting on her badge for show...

00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:53.320
You don't usually put that on
and go to school, do you?

00:16:53.790 --> 00:16:58.260
That violent girl
can't be saving lives, can she?

00:16:58.260 --> 00:17:00.570
I heard she saved a kid from drowning...

00:17:00.570 --> 00:17:03.500
